  "author": "@deyzunasbunker",
  "text": "My tip for newbies, to add to the video, is:\n\n- Pre-level 45 accounts: Just do a full set and dont worry about leveling (since all you're getting is the mainstat).\nIf you're struggling, then maybe upgrade just your main DPS covenant.\n\n- Level 45 account: Now, if a wheel that you know is good (like Burial Grounds) has pieces with good MAINstats, then upgrade it and don't worry about substats until much later.\nFocus on having a general wheel for everybody first with good MAINstats.\n\nGreat video!",
